Class AbstractDimensionsSelectingDistanceFunction<V extends FeatureVector<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.distance.distancefunction.subspace.AbstractDimensionsSelectingDistanceFunction<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of FeatureVector to compute the distances in between
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DistanceFunction<V>, PrimitiveDistanceFunction<V>, DimensionSelectingSubspaceDistanceFunction<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SubspaceLPNormDistanceFunction

    public abstract class AbstractDimensionsSelectingDistanceFunction<V extends FeatureVector<?>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrimitiveDistanceFunction<V>, DimensionSelectingSubspaceDistanceFunction<V>
    Abstract base class for distances computed only in subspaces. Selected dimensions are encuded as bits in a long[].
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    Elke Achtert
